org.ensembl.variation.datamodel
Interface VariationFeature

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable, Feature, Locatable, Persistent, java.io.Serializable
public interface VariationFeature
extends Feature

This is a an occurrence of a nucleotide variation in the genome. The actual variation information is represented by an associated Variation object. Some of the information has been denormalized and is available on the feature for speed purposes.

Author:
Craig Melsopp
See Also:
Variation
